      <Placemark>
        <name>Maders Slaghuis</name>
        <description><![CDATA[A butcher that sells biltong, a salted dried meat. Afrikaner paraphernalia hangs in the shop, which bothered Tony. For restaurant, you can go to the meat counter and order cuts of meat with "monkey gland sauce" on the side (barbecue sauce).]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
