          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Robot Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony said this was the greatest show he's ever seen, better than Jimi Hendrix, Janis Joplin, and David Bowie live. He saw the show called Robot Wars.]]></description>
