      <Placemark>
        <name>Erguang Wonton (Zhaozhou Road)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony's dinner guest, English teacher Bill Wang, says this is the best place to get wontons. Minced pork, bok choy, rice wine in a wonton dough, served with a mixture of soy sauce, vinegar, chili sauce, sesame oil, and peanut butter. "YOU NEED THIS," Tony exclaims.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-C2185B</styleUrl>
        <Point>
