      <Placemark>
        <name>Iglesia Divino Niño Jesus en Asuncion Paraguay</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony visited this old cemetery to see if he could find his great great great great grandfather's grave. He did not find it but historians said it might have been overbuilt. While in Paraguay he learned that his ancestor came into the country as a hat maker but also sold fireworks, which could have been made into weapons.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1556-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -57.5902012,-25.2939234,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
