        <name><![CDATA[Frank's Deli & Restaurant]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[Tony had a Jersey sandwich with sliced ham, salami, pepperoni, provolone, tomato, onions, shredded lettuce, roasted peppers, and oil & vinegar.]]></description>
