            110.354318,1.5527309,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Kuching</name>
        <description>Tony returned to the small village of Kuching nearly a decade since his last visit. “When I first went up this river, I was sick with love—the bad kind, the fist around your heart kind. I ran far, but there was no escaping it. It followed me up river, all the way. That was 10 long years ago. … Yet here I am again, heading up to that same longhouse in the jungle.”</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1523-FF5252</styleUrl>
        <Point>
